Titolo: Bomberman Land (Wii)

Anno: 2007

Descrizione: Bomberman Land (also known as Bomberman Land Wii) is an action puzzle video game developed and published by Hudson Soft. It was released in Japan for Wii on March 8, 2007, January 29, 2008 in North America, and March 14, 2008 in Europe. Part of the Bomberman franchise, it is the fifth game in the Bomberman Land series and the console counterpart to the portable version released for the PlayStation Portable later in the same month.